These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-1::.
There 2 different types of food: asparagus, garlic
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, boat
1. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person eating asparagus is not to the right of the person driving the boat##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |
| Food        | asparagus   | garlic   |
| Transport   | boat | bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, cola
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, tennis
1. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
2. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | cola | fanta   |
| Sport      | tennis | soccer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-3::.
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, kiwi
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, house
1. the person eating eggplant is not to the left of the fan of house##8
2. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Food          | kiwi | eggplant |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | house     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-8-4::.
